@startuml sequence_register
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Register New Equipment

actor "Fleet Manager" as FM
participant "Angular SPA" as SPA
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "Equipment Controller" as Ctrl
participant "Equipment Service" as Svc
database "SQL Database" as DB

FM -> SPA: Click "Add Equipment"
SPA -> SPA: Show registration form
FM -> SPA: Fill form + Submit
SPA -> SPA: Client-side validation
SPA -> GW: POST /api/v1/equipment\n{name, make, model, year,\nserialNumber, category, status}
GW -> Ctrl: Forward (authenticated)
Ctrl -> Ctrl: Validate request\n(FluentValidation)
Ctrl -> Svc: CreateEquipmentCommand
Svc -> DB: Check serial number\nuniqueness in org
DB --> Svc: No duplicate found
Svc -> DB: INSERT Equipment
DB --> Svc: Equipment created
Svc --> Ctrl: EquipmentDto
Ctrl --> GW: 201 Created\n+ Location header
GW --> SPA: Equipment response
SPA --> FM: Redirect to\nequipment detail page

@enduml
